title: Beauty and the Beast 2012 S04E01 WS.XviD-err0001
description:
Beauty and the Beast (2012) S04E01 - Monsieur et Madame Bete

Vincent and Cat learn that someone is trying to expose the identities of the beasts, and Tess is reluctant to help find out who is behind the threat.

This episode aired on May 29, 2016 on Showcase Canada, 4 days ahead of the US broadcast. Like all of my releases to date, the source is an analog rip, so the quality is, at best, something like A8 V8. 

To leave comments/questions for me, use KAT or TPB.

Enjoy!
